# wandb server stop

## 

​

Usage
    
    
    stop [OPTIONS]
    

## 

​

Description

Stop a running local W&B server. Stops the Docker container named `wandb-local` that was started by `wandb server start`. Requires Docker to be installed. For example, to stop the local W&B server:
    
    
    wandb server stop
    

